description:
The first ever dog catalog of over 100 dog breeds for HP WebOS! 

This free application provides different types of dog breeds accompanied with its picture, characteristics and best of all its favorite foods!

We have surveyed over 100 dog owners for each specific dog breed to find out what their breed's favorite foods are!

If you have a pet dog, this app is no doubt a-must-be-installed in your WebOS devices. 

You can also use this application to look through different type of breeds and help you decide on your future or new pet dog!

If you have any other breeds that are not listed, you can visit our website support and we will get another round of surveys and update the app!

Enjoy!

What's new in v.1.0.6?
- Fixed letter M button
- Added the most highly requested breed: The American Pitbull Terrier.
